### Gateway 기본 주소 (로컬)
@origin = http://localhost:8080

### ============================================
### 1. httpbin-get: /get -> https://httpbin.org
### ============================================
GET {{origin}}/get
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 2. local-api: /api/** -> http://localhost:8081
### (8081에서 백엔드 서비스가 떠 있어야 함)
### ============================================
GET {{origin}}/api/hello
Accept: application/json

###

GET {{origin}}/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### ============================================
### 3. httpbin-delay: /delay/** -> https://httpbin.org
### (지연 응답 테스트, 기본 0초)
### ============================================
GET {{origin}}/delay/0
Accept: application/json

###

### 3초 지연 후 응답
GET {{origin}}/delay/3
Accept: application/json

###
